        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Administrative Law Judges Competitive Service Restoration Act</strong></p> <p>This bill&nbsp;makes administrative law judge (ALJ)&nbsp;positions&nbsp;part of the competitive service and&nbsp;otherwise&nbsp;modifies the process for the appointment of ALJs, including by establishing certain minimum qualifications and conditions of employment. </p>]]>
        </text>
